**make spot_mini_mini run**

https://github.com/OpenQuadruped/spot_mini_mini#how-to-run delivers no details so here they are:

sudo apt install gazebo9-common libgazebo9-dev gazebo9 ros-melodic-gazebo-ros-pkgs ros-melodic-gazebo-dev ros-melodic-gazebo-ros-control ros-melodic-gazebo-ros ros-melodic-urdf-sim-tutorial ros-melodic-simulatorssudo apt-get

install ros-melodic-desktop-full

mkdir catkin_ws  
cd catkin_ws/  
mkdir ~/catkin_ws/src  
cd ~/catkin_ws/src  
git clone https://github.com/OpenQuadruped/spot_mini_mini.git  
cd ..  
catkin_make  
source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash  
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-joy  


python3 -m venv spot_mini_venv  
source spot_mini_venv/bin/activate  
pip3 install rospkg  
pip3 install gym  
pip3 install pyyaml  
pip3 install scipy  
pip3 install pybullet  
pip3 install torch  

roslaunch mini_ros spot_move.launch  
